title: Living With Confidence | Joel Osteen

description:
If you want to reach your destiny, you have to learn to see yourself the way God sees you. You have royal blood flowing through your veins! 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
